		y: -0.5d
		dependencies: ["0000000000030019"]
		title: "Exalted Orb"
		icon: {id: "mmorpg:currency/upgrade_common_affix", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Forge an Exalted Orb in the Quantum Exaltation Array. Upgrades one Common-tier affix on a Rare item to a higher rarity tier — not a reroll, not a gamble, a targeted upgrade. Gate: Mythic Stone + Map Completion Token + ZPM Circuit."]
