		title: "Orb of Introspection"
		icon: {id: "mmorpg:currency/base_number_reroll", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Forge an Orb of Introspection in the Quantum Exaltation Array. Rerolls the base stat values on any piece of gear — not the affixes, the underlying base stats the item rolled with. Gate: Mythic Stone + Map Completion Token + ZPM Mainframe."]
